text: Christine P. Barnetson was a swimmer from Australia. Barnetson competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics. She was born on 5 March 1948 and died on 19 June 2019.Christine Barnetson == References == Category:1948 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Australian swimmers Category:Olympians for Australia Category:Sportspeople from Perth, Western Australia
